  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink28-kilavi">
        <p type="edition"> iṟceṟivitta iṭattuk talaimakaṭku eytiya vēṟupāṭu kaṇṭu, ‘itu teyvattiṉāṉ
          āyiṟṟu’ eṉṟu tamar veṟiyeṭuppuḻi ataṉai vilakkak karutiya tōḻi cevilikku aṟattoṭu niṉṟatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink28">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> uṇṭuṟai yaṇaṅkiva ḷuṟainō yāyiṟ</l>
          <l> ṟaṇcēṟu kaḷvaṉ varikku mūraṟ</l>
          <l> koṇṭoṭi nekiḻac cāay</l>
          <l> meṉṟōḷ pacappa tevaṉko laṉṉāy.</l>

        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l> If it's because of a spirit from the drinking ghat that she's still in pain, </l>
          <l> [then] what about the fading of [her] soft shoulders? </l>
          <l> Or the fact that she's so spent that [her] bright bangles loosen? </l>
          <l> –[all] because of the man from the village where crabs scratch [lines] into the cool
            mud? </l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
